  "prompt": "Do we get condoms in different sizes in Mumbai?",
  "response": "Yes, condoms are available in different sizes in Mumbai, just as they are in other parts of India and the world. Most condom brands offer a range of sizes to ensure a comfortable and secure fit. Common sizes include:\n\n1. **Small** - For a snug fit.\n2. **Regular** - The standard size, suitable for most people.\n3. **Large** - For a looser, more comfortable fit.\n\nYou can find condoms of various sizes at pharmacies, supermarkets, and online platforms like Amazon, Flipkart, and specialty health stores. Brands like **Durex**, **Kamasutra**, **Manforce**, and **Skore** are popular in India and offer a variety of sizes.\n\nIf you\u2019re unsure about which size to choose, it\u2019s always a good idea to try a few options to find the one that fits best. Proper fit is important for both comfort and effectiveness.",
